		(property "Description" "Talk series resistor and K1 handshake bridge (2.2k): TALK_BRIDGE -> R28 -> TX_OUT. With K1 closed, P2 -> TALK_BRIDGE -> R28 -> TX_OUT -> P3 is the V4.1 talk handshake; codec TX joins TALK_BRIDGE through R26/C14. Kept at 2.2k to match the WF26 talk resistor and remain distinct from the near-short that fires the door opener."
