		(property "Description" "Omron G6K-2F-Y DC12 SMD DPDT latch relay, 12V coil ~1.315k. Coil pin1=K5_LATCH (+), pin8=P1/GND; primary pole COM3=K5_COM_RLY, NO4=K5_LATCH, NC2 unused; auxiliary pole COM6=GND, NO5=K5_SENSE, NC7 unused. Raw P4 reaches K5_LATCH through normally-closed K6; after a Türruf pulse the primary pole seals the coil from P2. D1 is the coil flyback clamp."
			(at 0 0 270)
			(unlocked yes)
			(layer "F.Fab")
