		(property "Description" "P4 isolation PhotoMOS (1-Form-B NC): bridges raw P4 to K5_LATCH at rest and without board power. Once K5's auxiliary contact proves the relay has pulled in, ISO_REQ energises K6 to open that bridge, preventing this apartment's P4 gong from feeding back onto P2 while K5 remains sealed from P2. Loss of K5 immediately interrupts the LED return and restores the normally-closed P4 path."
